high_descs: Turn left and go straight, and turn right to go toward the kitchen island.
Pick up the spoon on the bottom right corner of the kitchen island.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn right to go toward the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Turn left, to face the direction of the dishwasher.
Put the spoon in the drawer located beneath the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn left, cross the room, hang a right at the edge of the counters to your left and head to the island counter on your right.
Pick up the silver spoon from the right edge of the counter top.
Turn around, walk towards the counter, hang a right before you reach the white dishwasher and head to the silver sink.
Place the spoon inside the sink to the right of the apple, fill the sink with water to clean it and pick up the spoon from the sink.
Turn to the left and open the short wide drawer in front of the lettuce under the counter top.
Place the spoon inside the drawer on the left side and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spoon in a wide drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the small counter by the dark stool
Pick up the small silver spoon from the counter
Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink
Put the spoon in the sink, wash it, and remove it
Turn left to face toward the other side of the counter
Open the top drawer by the lettuce and put the spoon in it
anns.task_desc: Put the washed spoon in the kitchen drawer
